Notes: SP's Heuer and Kraemer become 13th and 14th players in school history to score
1,000 career points...SP pushed lead to 59-49 with 9:23 left in second half
before UW-Stout used 12-4 run to cut lead to 63-61 with 4:25 left...SP made
seven of next eight free throws to pull away...SP ranked 8th by D3hoops.com.
